    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The exterior is clean overall, showing only minor surface wear and small paint chips typical for its age, while the interior remains comfortable, tidy, and free of any major stains or tears. Mechanically, the car is solid, providing a smooth ride and reliable performance for daily commuting or longer trips. Prospective buyers can expect a dependable vehicle that is ready to drive immediately without the need for urgent repairs.",
