    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in showroom state. Meticulously preserved and mechanically peerless, it offers a rare opportunity for the collector or enthusiast who demands perfection. Every detail, from the pristine undercarriage to the factory-fresh upholstery, underscores its unrivaled status in the current market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
