    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am absolutely thrilled to show you this beauty. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly spectacular, showroom-ready condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels brand new! It drives like an absolute dream and has been pampered in a garage since day one. I\u2019m looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved. You\u2019ve got to see it in person to believe how clean it is. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
