    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS to deliver linear power up to an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory GKN limited-slip differential, the mechanical engagement is unparalleled. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable damping rates. This example boasts a documented service history including preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly is in peak operating condition. The exterior finish and interior upholstery are flawless, reflecting a strictly climate-controlled life.",
